column5: Intro;  Hello to all, just wanted to introduce my self, long time lurker, 1st time joiner, just wanted to say hello to all, and that this is a great board here. Personally I fish for everything, Trout, Pickeral, Bass, Pike, Panfish ect…. All year long – from January through the ice (for anything) to spring and summer panfish, Pickeral and Bass, to fall Steelies, Browns, and Ho’s…. if it swims in Ontario I fish for it.  It’s great to Join!!!!
You've got a lot of flair
Welcome to the forum. It's a great spot.
Welcome aboard! No, I don't have a case of the Mondays.
^---- Rich always has a case of the Mondays  :)
Hey when you work retail days off are never the same, any day can be my 'Monday'! Lol
Thanks guys, yeah everyday I go in the office it feels like a case of the Mondays.
welcome aboard......we dont always fight i swear....
